reviewText: The Thomas & Friends "stories" are a staple at our house to "wind-down" near bedtime.  We have seen all of them lots of times.
If you child is a Thomas's fan then you wouldn't go wrong buying this. An other set of good stories.

This DVD is GREAT! My 2.5 year old LOVES it because it focuses on the other engines besides Thomas: James, Emily, et al. It has two really cool songs that are featured on the "Songs from the Station" DVD. A must-have!!!
